=Dragon Warrior (NES) SRAM Map=

Dragon Warrior uses 8KB of battery-backed SRAM located at $6000-$7fff for save game data. The game supports a single save file with comprehensive player progress tracking.

==Save Game Structure==

The save game data begins at $6000 and uses the following structure:

