!  Offset  !!  Size  !!  Type  !!  Description
|-
|  $6000  ||  1 byte  ||  Flag  ||  Save file validity flag ($a5 = valid save)
|-
|  $6001  ||  1 byte  ||  Level  ||  Player level (1-30)
|-
|  $6002  ||  2 bytes  ||  HP  ||  Current HP (little endian)
|-
|  $6004  ||  2 bytes  ||  MP  ||  Current MP (little endian)
|-
|  $6006  ||  1 byte  ||  STR  ||  Strength stat
|-
|  $6007  ||  1 byte  ||  AGI  ||  Agility stat
|-
|  $6008  ||  2 bytes  ||  EXP  ||  Current experience points (little endian)
|-
|  $600a  ||  2 bytes  ||  GOLD  ||  Current gold amount (little endian)
|-
|  $600c  ||  1 byte  ||  WEAPON  ||  Equipped weapon ID
|-
|  $600d  ||  1 byte  ||  ARMOR  ||  Equipped armor ID
|-
|  $600e  ||  1 byte  ||  SHIELD  ||  Equipped shield ID
|-
|  $600f  ||  1 byte  ||  MAP  ||  Current map ID
|-
|  $6010  ||  1 byte  ||  X_POS  ||  Player X position on map
|-
|  $6011  ||  1 byte  ||  Y_POS  ||  Player Y position on map
|-
|  $6012  ||  1 byte  ||  DIRECTION  ||  Player facing direction (0=up, 1=right, 2=down, 3=left)
|-
|  $6013  ||  8 bytes  ||  NAME  ||  Player name (8 characters, space-padded)
|-
|  $601b  ||  32 bytes  ||  ITEMS  ||  Inventory items (item ID per byte, $ff = empty slot)
|-
|  $603b  ||  16 bytes  ||  FLAGS  ||  Game progress flags (quest items, story progress)
|-
|  $604b  ||  16 bytes  ||  SPELLS  ||  Known spells bitmask
|-
|  $605b  ||  1 byte  ||  CHECKSUM  ||  Save data checksum
|-
|  $605c-$7fff  ||  ...  ||  UNUSED  ||  Unused SRAM space
|}

